<para>Loads a font from the specified path and caches glyphs within the given character range. The font can later be referenced by its `FontId` when creating `TextRenderCommand` objects.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>fontId</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
